    {
      "id": "p002",
      "index": 2,
      "source": "Microsoft also detailed their die-to-die (D2D) interconnect. Their test vehicle includes two dies and two pairs of D2D nodes for interconnection. A full mock-up of the power delivery network and routing were included to mimic clock gating and crosstalk.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0290",
